==============================================================================================================
  base_class_specifier          |           Public                    protected                    private
==============================================================================================================
1.Public base_class_name        |           public                    protected                    private

2.protected base_class_name     |           protected                 protected                    private

3.private base_class_name       |           private                   private                      private
==============================================================================================================

private base_class_name =>
private, protected and public members of base class , all become private members in derived class;
i.e. derived class treat the members variables as thier own private members variables.